## Agent Rules

<!--
Hard rules that prevent known friction patterns. These override agent defaults.
-->

- When moving files, ALWAYS update import paths in the moved files AND in all files that import them. Run the test suite before reporting success.
- When a test fails after file changes, check import paths FIRST — broken relative imports after file moves are the most common root cause.
- Do NOT guess API names or config keys — grep the codebase or check docs. If unsure, ask rather than trying 3 wrong approaches.

